<br>
A RA that I thought would make RVR more interesting and fit into the &quot;Guild of Shadows&quot; motif would be to give Mercs a &quot;Hide&quot; RA (costs 10 points on a 30 minute timer). Mercs can only activate this stealth ability if they aren't in combat/targetted by enemies and remain immobile. This lasts for up to 10 minutes or should the Merc move or attack a target.  <br>
<br>
For those that don't want to have any ability similar to Infs, then here's another one. &quot;Disarm&quot;  RA, 10 points on a 15 minute timer. When used, your enemy's main weapon slot is switched to a separate slot ie switched from Right hand or 2-hand slot to the short/long/crossbow slot. This ability would hinder/disrupt enemy tanks, but wouldn't be overly overpowering since all they have to do is hotkey the appropriate weapon again. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kerrecsnowmane>Kerrec Snowmane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 114<br> <font color=#000000>(6/27/03 2:26 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=268.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Unique RA</span><hr size=1> We already have plenty of styles, and our hotbars have enough timers on them.  <br>
<br>
Void is a 10 pt style with a 10 minute timer.  Doesn't matter how high the To-Hit and Damage is, or that it has Medium Defense...there's no place on our hotbars and it's not worth buying.<br>
<br>
We have plenty of styles already, don't need more.<br>
<br>
Change Void (and other light tank class specific RA's) and make it into a Weaponskill boost (100 pts, or whatever is deemed balanced) that also halves your style endurance use for it's duration (whatever is deemed balanced).  Something like that would start to make a 10 point RA worth buying.<br>
<br>
