<br>
Here was my idea for a class RA change for us.<br>
<br>
<br>
It seems that there's roughly the same number of mercs that have our class RA Void (read: overpriced style usable once every fight or 2) as there are with shield spec greater than 23. Not very many. There's also very few that have Bladedance, though many seem to express interrest in it till they see the price tag. My proposal is to try and get Bladedance changed to our class RA (possibly sharable with the other light tanks, much as Archers all get True Sight). With this change would come a removal, or lessening of the pre-req (aug dex 3 is a bit steep), and perhaps a lessening of the cost from 14 pts to 10 or even 12. If it were to stay at 14 points I think the timer should be halved at least.  Either way I think for an RA that expensive the damage needs to be equal to a caster PBAOE (not like we can spam it unless ya get a group full of mercs, hmmmmm... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :evil --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/images/emoticons/devil.gif ALT=":evil"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> )<br>
