I think a good unique ability would be something that fits in along the lines of a mercenary, guild of shadows etc such as<br>
<br>
1) 30 min Small AOE dirt 10 second fumble - useful when the zerg goes charging through you. Would reduce the damage for 10 seconds. People might bitch that this plus BOF is too much.<br>
